# astrion-skill v1
goal: Permanently delete everything in Trash
trigger:
  - phrase: "empty trash"
  - phrase: "clear trash"
when:
  - "There is at least one file in /Trash"
do: |
  List all files and folders in /Trash. For each, permanent-delete via
  the underlying filesystem API (NOT the trash-move — these are
  already in trash). Show a notification with the count of items
  deleted and the total size freed.
constraints:
  level: L2
  budget_tokens: 200
  reversibility: NONE
